modelCars.name: Bburago KTM 250 Duke
modelCars.description:
This KTM 250 Duke diecast model motorcycle is orange/black and features working wheels. It is made by Bburago and is 1:18 scale (approx. 12cm / 4.7in long).

The KTM Duke 250 is a great all round morotcyle - making it incredibly popular with motorcycle enthusiasts. This model is a faithful replica - perfect for any model bike collection.
